# TaskFlow Backend — Implementation Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete, production-ready REST API for TaskFlow covering **all 8 functional modules** from [TASKFLOW_DOCS.md](file:///d:/Developments/College%20Project/TASKFLOW_DOCS.md).

---

## File Structure (Final)

```
taskflow-backend/
├── server.js                         # HTTP entry point with graceful shutdown
├── src/
│   ├── app.js                        # Express + Socket.IO wiring
│   ├── controllers/
│   │   ├── authController.js         # register, login, refresh (rotation), logout, OTP reset
│   │   ├── taskController.js         # 8 handlers + socket emit + notifications
│   │   ├── notesController.js        # 9 handlers (pages + blocks)
│   │   ├── calendarController.js     # 4 handlers
│   │   ├── teamController.js         # 2 handlers
│   │   ├── notificationController.js # 3 handlers (with since-timestamp)
│   │   └── userController.js         # dashboard aggregation + profile
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── taskService.js            # Delegation rules, status transitions
│   │   ├── notesService.js           # Tree builder, ownership validation
│   │   └── notificationService.js   # DB insert + real-time emit
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── userModel.js              # Full user + refresh token CRUD
│   │   ├── taskModel.js              # Full task CRUD + delegation
│   │   ├── notesModel.js             # Pages (UUID) + blocks + BFS delete
│   │   ├── calendarModel.js          # Events + combined month query
│   │   ├── teamModel.js              # Members with task counts + activity
│   │   └── notificationModel.js     # Notifications + unread count
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── authRoutes.js             # /auth/* with Joi + rate limiters
│   │   ├── taskRoutes.js             # /tasks/*
│   │   ├── notesRoutes.js            # /notes/pages/* + /notes/blocks/*
│   │   ├── calendarRoutes.js         # /calendar/events/*
│   │   ├── teamRoutes.js             # /team/*
│   │   ├── notificationRoutes.js     # /notifications/*
│   │   └── userRoutes.js             # /dashboard + /users/me
│   ├── middleware/
│   │   ├── auth.js                   # JWT Bearer token verify
│   │   ├── errorHandler.js           # AppError class + catch-all handler
│   │   ├── rateLimiter.js            # 100/min general + 5/15min auth strict
│   │   └── validate.js               # Joi validation middleware factory
│   └── utils/
│       ├── db.js                     # mysql2 connection pool (max 20)
│       ├── jwt.js                    # generateTokens, verifyToken, verifyRefreshToken
│       ├── asyncWrapper.js           # Wraps async handlers for error propagation
│       ├── otpStore.js               # In-memory OTP (10 min TTL, 3 attempts, 15 min lockout)
│       ├── mailer.js                 # Nodemailer + sendOtpEmail
│       ├── socket.js                 # Socket.IO singleton + emitToUser
│       └── migrate.js                # Migration runner
├── migrations/
│   └── 001_initial_schema.sql        # All 6 tables
└── seeds/
    └── seed.js                       # 5 users, tasks, notes, events, notifications
```

