## Setup Instructions

```bash
# 1. Copy and fill in your env file
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your MySQL credentials and JWT secrets

# 2. Create database
mysql -u root -p -e "CREATE DATABASE taskflow;"

# 3. Run migrations
npm run migrate

# 4. (Optional) Seed dev data  — test password: "password123"
npm run seed

# 5. Start dev server
npm run dev
```

---

## API Base URL: `/api/v1`

| Module | Routes |
|--------|--------|
| **Auth** | `POST /auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/auth/refresh`, `/auth/logout`, `/auth/reset-password`, `/auth/reset-password/verify` |
| **Tasks** | `GET/POST /tasks`, `GET/PUT/DELETE /tasks/:id`, `PATCH /tasks/:id/status`, `PATCH /tasks/:id/delegate`, `DELETE /tasks` (bulk) |
| **Notes** | `GET/POST /notes/pages`, `GET/PUT/DELETE /notes/pages/:id`, `POST /notes/pages/:id/blocks`, `PUT/DELETE /notes/blocks/:id`, `PATCH /notes/pages/:id/reorder` |
| **Calendar** | `GET/POST /calendar/events`, `PUT/DELETE /calendar/events/:id` |
| **Team** | `GET /team`, `GET /team/:id/activity` |
| **Notifications** | `GET /notifications`, `PATCH /notifications/read-all`, `PATCH /notifications/:id/read` |
| **Dashboard** | `GET /dashboard` |
| **User** | `GET /users/me`, `PATCH /users/me` |

---

## Key Edge Cases Handled

| Edge Case | Implementation |
|-----------|---------------|
| Refresh token reuse | Delete all tokens for user → force re-login |
| Duplicate email on register | `409 Conflict` |
| OTP expiry / wrong / lockout | In-memory OTP store, 422 with reason |
| Mark task done with pending subtasks | 409 with blocking task titles |
| Delegate to yourself | 400 Bad Request |
| Delegate a done task | 409 Conflict |
| Bulk delete non-owned tasks | Silently skip, return `{ deleted, skipped }` |
| Delete notes page with children | BFS recursive delete |
| Notification catch-up on reconnect | `GET /notifications?since=<timestamp>` |
| Online/offline status | Updated via Socket.IO connect/disconnect |
| Calendar month + task due dates | Combined query in [getEventsForMonth](file:///d:/Developments/College%20Project/taskflow-backend/src/models/calendarModel.js#22-47) |

