## Socket.IO Events

| Event | Direction | Trigger |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| `task:assigned` | Server → Client | New task created |
| `task:delegated` | Server → Client | Task delegated |
| `task:updated` | Server → Client | Status or field change |
| `notification:new` | Server → Client | Any notification created |
| `user:online` | Broadcast | User connects |
| `user:offline` | Broadcast | User disconnects |
